criteria.textblock:
        Training and validation cohort

        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age more than 18 years;

          -  fulfilled diagnosis of cACLD based on radiological, histological features of liver
             cirrhosis

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  prior liver decompensation;

          -  hepatocellular carcinoma;

          -  prior liver transplantation;

          -  portal vein thrombosis;

          -  antiplatelet or anticoagulation;

          -  without screening EGD within six months of TE;

          -  incomplete follow-up data.

        HVPG cohort

        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age more than 18 years;

          -  fulfilled diagnosis of cACLD based on radiological, histological features of liver
             cirrhosis

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  prior liver decompensation;

          -  hepatocellular carcinoma;

          -  prior liver transplantation;

          -  portal vein thrombosis;

          -  antiplatelet or anticoagulation;

          -  without screening EGD within six months of TE;

          -  without HVPG measurement;

          -  non-sinusoidal portal hypertension.
